Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.86,1:11:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,了解  猎手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.45,1:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.26,1:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you  海苔
